Summarise this sleep data. Provide the date, duration, start/end times, and a breakdown of sleep phases (deep/light/rem/awake).

* GUARDRAILS

Output as JSON with the exact following fields:
 - date - The date of the sleep log
 - duration - The total duration (e.g., 8h 15min)
 - start_time - Start time (HH:MM)
 - end_time - End time (HH:MM)
 - deep_sleep - Total deep sleep duration (e.g., 3h 0min)
 - phases - A summary of deep/light/rem sleep
 - summary - A brief one-sentence qualitative observation of the sleep quality.
